headline: Assessing Smurfit Westrock (SW) After Recent Integration Updates And Mixed Share Price Performance
summary: If you are wondering whether Smurfit Westrock at around US$41.63 is a bargain or just fairly priced, you are not alone. The stock has had a mixed run, with a 5% gain over the last 30 days, a 5% year to date return, but a 1 year return of an 18.4% decline and a 3 year return of 6.9%. Recent news flow around Smurfit Westrock has centered on its progress as a combined packaging group and how the integration is shaping investor expectations.
